<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I lampiu ah I kipahna din la sai tiu,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu;
 Zan hung bei in tin kumsawt khuo hungvak ta'n a,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu.

[V2]
 Chawmlo kal sungin, chawmlo kalsung in,
 Tui kinawk galkai hiting;
 Buoina huihpi hat a beih tieng kituok hitiu,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu.

[V3]
 2. I khutun na sem hitiu I theihtawp suoh in,
 Chawmlo kalin Van In tung hitiu;
 Pathien lungsietna'n ei hihhat thak zel intin,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Lampi siem zang hitiu, kengkham chaute hawh di'n,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu;
 Hehpih lunggil pun, thupha chuh gen viel hitiu,
 Chawmlo kal in van In tung hitiu.

[V5]
 4. Buoina cheng khelah kumsawt chawlhna nuom a-um,
 Chawmlo kalin van in tung hitiu;
 Khawpi vak hawih achun mitthi cheng hul ta'n a,
 Chawmlo kalin van In tung hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>WHILE WE ARE GOING HOME</title>
<hymn_number>403</hymn_number>
</song>